txt.en: Edenos is at the Palace of Eldacar.\n\nYou should speak to Edenos.

'The time has come for a covert mission. I'm sending you behind enemy lines, soldier. The Orcs have supplies to help repair some of their damaged siege equipment. I'm sure you understand we can't let that happen.\n\n'Use some stealth when you're out there. Destroying those supply crates will weaken their efforts to take the city from us.'
Edenos has tasked you with destroying the enemies supplies in order to weaken their efforts to take the city.
'You have done much for the Gondorian army. We will take back this city!'
Enemy supplies can be found on the Eastern side of Osgiliath.\n\nYou should destroy enemy supplies.
